snippet.title: Chesstle Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The Trailer for the demo of our upcoming game Chesttle. You can find it on steam as we are participating in Steamwork's Autumn Edition Festival (7-13 October) !

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1401620/Chesstle/

Also Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/M7WNwE
